                            </FooterDetails>
                            <Heading/>
                            <Paragraph>The Multilateral Investment Guarantee Agency (MIGA),
                                        a World Bank Group institution, was formally constituted in
                                        1988.</Paragraph>
                        </Detail>
                        <Detail SortOrder="2" TypeOfProgramAndActivitiesDetailsId="2050">
                            <FooterDetails>
                                <Email/>
                                <Footer/>
                                <WebAddress>https://www.miga.org/who-we-are</WebAddress>
                            </FooterDetails>
                            <Heading/>
                            <Paragraph>Working with public and private insurers, MIGA
                                        promotes foreign direct investment in developing countries
                                        to support economic growth, reduce poverty, and improve the
                                        quality of people's lives. Due to its status as a World Bank
                                        Group institution, MIGA's guarantees protect investments
                                        against noncommercial risks and help investors gain access
                                        to funding sources with improved financial terms and
                                        conditions.</Paragraph>
                        </Detail>
                    </Details>
                </Activity>
